Remington is well known for high quality hair tools at an affordable price. If you love to use heat tools on your hair with minimal damage, the brand has some great options. The Remington Shine Therapy Hair Straighteners are one of the products on offer, and they are currently on sale for £29.99, saving you 62 percent off the RRP price of £79.  The Dyson Corrale straighteners are also sold on Boots but for £399, which is 90 percent more expensive than the Remington version.   If you are a Boots cardholder, you can collect points with each item you purchase.  